name: auditRestrictionLevels
title: Audit Restriction Levels
description: Audit Event Restriction Levels for defining restriction levels related to non-citizens and non-guardians, used in the AuditEvent.securityLevel field.

concept.definition: Indicates the person is not a citizen, and thus has a restricted access level.
Indicates the person is not a legal guardian, and thus has a restricted access level.
